MOST IMMEDIATE
No. 1/34/1/2008-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 30th November, 2008
9 Agrahayana, 1930 (S)
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 30th
November, 2008:-
Shri Shivraj V. Patil relinquished the charge of the office of the
Minister of Home Affairs;
Shri P. Chidambaram relinquished the charge of the office of
the Minister of Finance and assumed the charge of the office of
the Minister of Home Affairs; and
The Prime Minister assumed the charge of the office of the
Minister of Finance.
i)
ii)
iii)
